---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Short explanation of Marquis Ladybug and the Field Archive series.">
  <main class="page">
    <section class="section split">
      <div>
        <p class="kicker">About</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-block">
        <h1 class="page-title">てんとうむし侯爵</h1>
        <p>
          Marquis Ladybug observes cities as Civilization OS field conditions: surfaces, routing, supply, residue, and motion.
        </p>
        <p>
          Urban Structure Study records hard infrastructure and operational forms. Urban Drift follows softer movement, light, and human traces.
        </p>
        <p>
          Planetary Runtime is related, but separate. It is the upper control surface; this site is the photographic archive.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
